metadata.name: Dirty Bitches Selfish Sofia 1 of 1
metadata.description:

Spend 5 minutes alone with Dirty Bitch Selfish Sofia and you will know what we are talking about! She unbelievably is the right-hand whore for a truly underhanded Dirty Bitch and the Boss Dirty Bitch Madam Ann! Your Dirty Bitches collection would not be complete without this Selfish Dirty Bitch.
